name: Cats and Cats and Cats - Sweet Drunk Everyone EP
description:
Tunbridge Wells/Staines 6 piece release their stunning post rock/indie/experimental over 45 minute long debut EP. Drowned In Sound have hailed them as ‘one of the best post-rock bands around’ find out what all the hype is about!

Tracklisting:

1. Every Handshake Is A Wolf.
2. Fight Fight With Fight.
3. Kites.
4. Hotel At The End Of Youth.
5. Splutterheart.

name: Collides In Arc - Collides In Arc Album
description:
Collides In Arc the album formally known as Seb Jenner releases his highly anticipated debut 12 track album, after touring and releasing a single earlier this year. The album creates stunning soundscapes and features beautiful cello, guitar and piano. Some of the most romantic music this miser has heard in years.
Tracklisting:

1) Paper Lantern
2) Lines in the Sky
3) Time to Think
4) Fingers Stretch
5) Shell Go Quietly
6) Some Songs…
7) Drop your head to the spinning of clouds.
8) I Fear Less Than This
9) Give me time, and ill leave soon 
10) Flower
11) A Man Alone
12) Cold Grip Against the Window

name: Tom Williams - Town Station Demos EP
description:
Tonbridge based twenty year old multi-instrumentalist singer/songwriter Tom Williams releases his debut 6 track ep, including three never heard before songs and featuring favorites ‘Denmark’, ‘Jazz Singer’ and ‘Train Station Car Park’! ‘Tunbridge Wells better watch out because Tom Williams is going to be big’ Chris T-T.

Tracklisting:
1. You Talk So Loudly On The Phone. 
2. Jazz Singer. 
3. Tried It, Easy, Go.
4. Train Station Carpark. 
5. Denmark. 
6. I Think You’re Doing Alright.
